title: La Victoria Red Taco Sauce, Mild, 15 Ounce
features: La Victoria red taco sauce, mild, 15 ounce
description: Shake up a bottle of red taco sauce, mild and turn your favorite dishes into culinary delights with a little bit of character and a whole lot of flavor. Red taco sauce, mild is gluten free and contains tomato puree (water and tomato paste), red California Chiles, onions, distilled vinegar, salt, jalapenos, modified food starch and Garli. In 1917, the la Victoria products were born with the jarring of the first salsa, la Victoria salsa Brava. And as folks responded to the fresh taste, we expanded the la Victoria product line to include taco sauces, enchilada sauces, jarred and canned chiles, peppers and more.
